RateMyApp - Class in com.ratemyapp
The RateMyApp class allows to create prompts appearing at the desired intervals, asking the user to review the app and to provide feedback to the developer.
RateMyAppListener - Interface in com.ratemyapp
The RateMyAppListener interface is responsible for being notified of visibility changes of the RateMyApp component.
reset() - Method in class com.ratemyapp.RateMyApp
Resets the counters of this component.
review() - Method in class com.ratemyapp.RateMyApp
Opens the review page within the Nokia Store client or, if not supported, within the device Web browser.
rmaComponentReady() - Method in interface com.ratemyapp.RateMyAppListener
Notifies that the RateMyApp component is ready to be used
rmaVisibilityChanged(boolean) - Method in interface com.ratemyapp.RateMyAppListener
Notifies visibility changes of the RateMyApp component
